The [[SmartRG SR905acv]] is identical but also has two VoIP ports.
The internal photos documents submitted to the FCC are just copies of the user manual.
===Features=== *Dual-band 802.11ac Wave 2 Access Point *4x4 MU-MIMO @5GHz, 4x4 SU-MIMO @2.4GHz *5x Gigabit Ethernet ports, 2x USB 3.0 ports *SFP slot for Gigabit FTTH broadband access *Two SIP-enabled FXS ports (SR905acv)
